    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I am so sad to see this beauty go, but it's time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it polished and pristine inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and is totally ready for your next big adventure. You seriously won't find another one this clean! Come take a look, I promise you\u2019re going to fall in love with it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
